body_html: I had trouble with these instructions for quite a while, I was still getting the 'Native TF methods not found' errors. After a while, I realized that the problem was my Android CPU was not arm-based, but rather x86_64. So, in my case, I used the awesome instructions from @matt-deboer, but replaced 'cpu=armeabi-v7a' with 'cpu=x86_64', and that resolved things for me.
